<style>
    h3 span {
        background:#FFF;
        padding:5px 15px 5px 15px;
    }
</style>

<div class="hero-unit">
    <div class="text-center">
      <img class="trex_logo" src="" alt="" />
      <br><br>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-center">
      <%= tr("Welcome to Tml For Ruby on Rails") %>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center">
        <%= tr("Tml for Ruby on Rails is a library that allows RoR based applications to integrate with the Translation Exchange crowd-sourced translation platform.") %>
        <%= tr("This sample application demonstrates some of Tml's capabilities.") %>
    </p>
    <br>
    <% unless tml_current_translator %>
        <p class="text-center">
            <a href="<%=tml_application.host%>/signup" class="btn btn-large"><%= tr('Sign up to get started now!') %></a>
        </p>
    <% end %>
</div>

<h3 class="hr strong"><span><%= tr("How It Works") %></span></h3>

<div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
        <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("how_it_works_1.gif") %></p>
        <h4 class="text-center"><%= tr("Use your users") %></h4>
        <p><%= tr("Your multilngual users can sign up to help translate your site into over 270 different languages.")%> <%= tr("Their translations can then be viewed and voted on by other users.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("how_it_works_2.gif") %></p>
        <h4 class="text-center"><%= tr("Share translations") %></h4>
        <p><%= tr("Translations from your site get synced to our servers and can then be shared with thousands of other websites.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("how_it_works_3.gif") %></p>
        <h4 class="text-center"><%= tr("Get what you give") %></h4>
        <p><%= tr("Regularly pull down new translations from not only your users but users of other websites as you sync your translations.") %></p>
    </div>
</div>

<h3 class="hr strong"><span><%= tr("Features") %></span></h3>

<div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Support for over 250 languages") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("All browser supported language are included. Just choose which languages you want to enabled on your app.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Inline translation tools") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Intuitive translation tools allow your users to easily translate your website.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Translation management") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Keep track of all the translated text on your website, through an easy to use dashboard.") %></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Translation ranking system") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Translators vote on translations and the best translations are used in your application.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Translator ranking system") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Translators are ranked based on the quality of the work they do. The higher the rank the more valuable they become.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Powerful Metrics") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Stay up to date on the progress of your translations.") %></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Translation Markup Language") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("TML syntax makes developers happy - it simplifies the code and allows to encode complex rules using simple structures.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Language Context Rules") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Tml supports all language rules to make translations very accurate.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Language Cases") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Language cases are supported across all languages to make translations sound as native as they can be.") %></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%= tr("Glossary") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Create a glossary of the key terms of your application. Translators will see those terms and will be able to provide more accurate translations.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Language Discussion Boards") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Translators can discuss translations and terms in the message boards across all languages.") %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span4">
        <h4><%=tr("Admin Tools") %></h4>
        <p><%=tr("Administration tools allow you to configure every aspect of your application.") %></p>
    </div>
</div>

<hr>
